flowchart TD
    U[Usuario: consulta NL + threshold] --> APP[Streamlit app.py]
    APP -->|play/pause, config| SCHED[Scheduler APScheduler]
    SCHED -->|cada N min| BOT[TradingBot orquestador]

    subgraph Screener
      BOT --> PLAN[Planner Haiku]
      PLAN -->|ScreenCriteria| UNI[get_universe]
      UNI --> DL[Descarga paralela asyncio]
      DL --> FUN[get_fundamentals]
      DL --> TEC[get_technicals]
      DL --> BEN[get_sector_benchmarks]
      FUN & TEC & BEN --> CACHE[(Cache DuckDB TTL)]
      FUN & TEC & BEN --> FILT[Filtros duros]
      FILT --> SCORE[Scoring 0-10]
      SCORE --> REAS[Reasoner Sonnet]
      REAS --> GUARD[Guardrail: verifica numeros]
    end

    GUARD -->|candidatos score>umbral| RISK[Risk: sizing max 5% + anti-duplicado]
    RISK -->|OrderRequest| ALP[Alpaca client paper]
    ALP --> ORD[(Orden ejecutada)]
    BOT --> LOG[(TradeLog DuckDB: ordenes, decisiones, equity)]

    ORD --> APP
    LOG --> APP
    APP --> POS[Posiciones + P&L]
    APP --> HIST[Historico de ordenes]
    APP --> EQ[Equity curve]
    APP --> TRACE[Logs/traza del agente]
